{"tid":347341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「警世」係香港千其唔好讀中藥！！！","createTime":"2017-08-04T17:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T13:33:34.000Z","uid":49128,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8fe900788df77ea9d441cc7bd785e73396b8f1","tid":347341,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"個ac借番黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有感而發<br />\n<br />\n就算你係香港讀中藥degree，ugc都好<br />\n<br />\n如果做唔到第三方公司就食得屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就註定同d得文憑、證書既阿姐一齊搵食<br />\n<br />\n人工仲一樣添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又比醫師點黎點去做隻狗<br />\n<br />\n醫師做錯野又唔可以屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n醫得好病人既，病人又多謝醫師唔係多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但有咩出錯就係你孭鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有準醫師（未考到牌）做執藥又有人請，人工仲高過二級配藥員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你話，做藥廠科研囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港有幾多藥廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本香港冇咩宜方面既工種比讀中藥既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係鐘意宜方面既，就讀中醫好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf974ead35df4345fff09471e2f7008120f7603c","tid":347341,"uid":49128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"想讀中藥既<br />\n<br />\n回頭是岸啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bb012742a9e080971e809cd7c466782fe50036","tid":347341,"uid":72638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"其實讀中醫都唔見得好景<br />\n僧多粥少<br />\n啲人又信唔過後生中醫"},{"pid":"49e2b3de4773ff92911b21d72c98298471cb06d8","tid":347341,"uid":49128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"D阿姐讀過文憑、證書都係同你做同一樣野炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26eef8b8fedf196a137b2c13725e4010ec71c724","tid":347341,"uid":49128,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實讀中醫都唔見得好景<br />\n僧多粥少<br />\n啲人又信唔過後生中醫</blockquote><br />\n中醫食一舊屎<br />\n中藥食三舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48149e3d8d66f73c0447c1de85ebd94060b537ec","tid":347341,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:45:12.000Z","msg":"中醫垃圾係常識嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7151ad6f8f4a714ed139dbf37a3e9e4fb6837e84","tid":347341,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中醫垃圾係常識嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解咁講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1d5f5a2bece2a9b5a0d978cbda1c884317c321","tid":347341,"uid":29464,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"中藥有degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nugc讀中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34e00a7c4c070fc58afaad0249c3f5252498ac8","tid":347341,"uid":49128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"讀曬銀時都千其唔好讀中藥啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkg